a|Cranberry Lake]], [[Dewdney, British Columbia|Dewdney]], [[Dufferin, British Columbia|Dufferin]], [[Fort Nelson, British Columbia|Fort Nelson]], [[Fraser Mills, British Columbia|Fraser Mills]], [[Glenmore, British Columbia|Glenmore]], [[Guisachan, British Columbia|Guisachan]], [[Kinnaird, British Columbia|Kinnaird]], [[Marysville, British Columbia|Marysville]], [[Matsqui, British Columbia|Matsqui]], [[Mission City, British Columbia|Mission City]], [[Natal, British Columbia|Natal]], [[Nicomen Island]], [[North Kamloops, British Columbia|North Kamloops]], [[Phoenix, British Columbia|Phoenix]], [[Point Grey, British Columbia|Point Grey]], [[Sandon, British Columbia|Sandon]], [[South Fort George, British Columbia|South Fort George]], [[South Vancouver, British Columbia|South Vancouver]], [[Sumas, British Columbia|Sumas]], [[Tadanac, British Columbia|Tadanac]], [[Valleyview, British Columbia|Valleyview]] and [[Westview, British Columbia|Westview]].<ref name=Others>{{cite web | url=http://www.bcstats.gov.bc.ca/StatisticsBySubject/Census/MunicipalPopulations.aspx | title=Municipal Census Populations (1921-2011) | publisher=BC Stats | accessdate=June 26, 2013 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121231000705/http://www.bcstats.gov.bc.ca/StatisticsBySubject/Census/MunicipalPopulations.aspx | archive-date=December 31, 2012 | url-status=dead }}</ref><ref name=Brocklehurst>{{cite web | url=http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/9883.html | title=Name Details: Brocklehurst (Community) | publisher=GeoBC | accessdate=June 27, 2013}}</ref><ref name=Columbia>{{cite web | url=http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/11640.html | title=Name Details: Grand Forks (City) | publisher=GeoBC | accessdate=May 4, 2014}}</ref><ref name=Dewdney>{{cite web | url=http://www.heritage-places.com/profiles/DewdneyComm.html | title=Profiles of Historic Sites: Dewdney Community | publisher=Mission District Historical Society, Heritage Places Branch | date=March 14, 2014 | accessdate=November 23, 2014}}</ref><ref name=Nicomen>{{cite web | url=http://www.heritage-places.com/profiles/NicIslComm.html | title=Profiles of Historic Sites: Nicomen Island Community | publisher=Mission District Historical Society, Heritage Places Branch | date=December 6, 2013 | accessdate=November 23, 2014}}</ref><ref name=Phoenix>{{cite web | url=http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/14193.html | title=Name Details: Phoenix (Abandoned Locality) | publisher=GeoBC | accessdate=June 27, 2013}}</ref><ref name=Sandon>{{cite web | url=http://www.sandonmuseum.ca/social-history/52-from-boom-to-bust-in-20-years | title=From Boom to Bust in 20 Years: Sandon's History as an Incorporated City | publisher=Sandon Museum | accessdate=June 26, 2013}}</ref> The majority of these former municipalities ceased to exist as a result of amalgamation with or annexation by another municipality.<ref name=Others/><ref name=Brocklehurst/><ref name=Columbia/> Others, such as Phoenix and Sandon,<ref name=Phoenix/><ref name=Sandon/> were dissolved from their municipal status as a result of population decline, while Dewdney dissolved due to financial reasons.<ref name=Dewdney/>\n\n== See also ==\n{{Portal|Canada}}\n*[[List of designated places in British Columbia]]\n*[[List of Haida villages]]\n*[[List of population centres in British Columbia]]\n\n== Notes ==\n{{notelist|30em}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n== External links ==\n*[http://www.cscd.gov.bc.ca/lgd/history/index.htm Local Government Department History]\n*[http://www.cscd.gov.bc.ca/lgd/gov_structure/library/local_gov_structure_managing_changes.pdf Managing Changes to Local Government Structure in British Columbia: A Review and Program Guide]\n*[http://www.gov.bc.ca/cscd Ministry of Community, Sport and Cultural Development]\n\n{{Navboxes\n| title = Links to related articles\n| state = expanded\n| list1  = {{Subdivisions of British Columbia|city=yes|town=yes|village=yes|district=yes}}\n{{Canada topic|List of municipalities in}}\n}}\n<noinclude>{{Featured list}}</noinclude>\n\n[[Category:Lists of populated places in British Columbia|Municipalities B]]\n[[Category:Municipalities in British Columbia|*]]\n", "name_user": "Alaney2k", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200etop:update outdated wlink, replaced: [[List of Canadian provinces and territories by population \u2192 [[Population of Canada by province and territory", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_municipalities_in_British_Columbia"}
